[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      123[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Amazon DynamoDB for prediction storage and real-time lookup.** Stores scored predictions with their explanations for fast lookup by claim ID. The billing system queries DynamoDB in real-time during claim creation to surface denial risk before submission. A GSI on `risk_score` enables the worklist engine to query all high-risk claims efficiently. Set TTL on prediction records based on your organization's retention policy: retain for the claim's appeal window (typically 60-180 days post-adjudication) plus an audit buffer. Archive to S3 Glacier for long-term compliance retention if needed.
